{"tid":2218983,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"藍絲狗加入kongu撕連儂牆","createTime":"2020-09-26T14:31:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-26T15:27:03.000Z","uid":188515,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"26c61d30e1ef34fd7225e5c2eeb055d244246c50","tid":2218983,"uid":188515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T14:31:13.000Z","msg":"港大學生會表示，晚上7時許，有大批不明人士闖入港大校園範圍內，撕毀三幅連儂牆，又推到學生會旗幟，其後離去。<br />\n<br />\n根據網上片段顯示，這批不明人士大多是中年男女，他們一邊搗亂，一邊高呼「我哋清理香港啲垃圾！清潔香港！」，其間夾雜大量粗言穢語，得手後往港大港鐵站方向揚長而去，當時有多名港大保安在場，他們沒有任由這批人離去，沒有阻止。<br />\n<br />\n另外有自稱是「香江同心會」的藍絲專頁上載影片，「炫耀」自己清拆連儂牆的「戰績」。片段所見，清拆文宣的不明人士至少有10人，他們趁現場沒有保安，快速撕毀連儂牆，其間拍攝片段的女性語帶鄉音，自稱是「無大檯、無機構、無錢攞」，更指出其行為是「我哋依家喺度清潔香港大學，我哋咁做係因為我哋唔希望自己嘅仔女喺咁唔乾淨嘅大學入面讀書」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b2EUeEK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb2EUeEK.png&h=54a04967&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KL8xLMt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKL8xLMt.png&h=d41037d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200926/RDRDZY3IZNFE3FGZDMFRATEY34/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200926%2FRDRDZY3IZNFE3FGZDMFRATEY34%2F&d=I0uz%2BNPXkLchxl3mN3HTu2zUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=89c5ec65\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200926%2FRDRDZY3IZNFE3FGZDMFRATEY34%2F&h=c6d0ffa8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200926/RDRDZY3IZNFE3FGZDMFRATEY34/</a>"},{"pid":"a4bee6ce87a9071708d851ec3373aa0a8617c150","tid":2218983,"uid":188515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T14:31:53.000Z","msg":"打多左個加字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"324a56363fcd5a0b56824e3f97d1f3405d9fc9a4","tid":2218983,"uid":171643,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T14:32:48.00